  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct used in posterior lumbar spinal fixation. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors are assessed; one factor (Test conditions) falls below the required level due to a single test condition being evaluated. Intended use is limited to Class II spinal implant regulatory submissions under 21 CFR 888.3076. Model risk level is 3 (substantial influence on device design decision). Decision: Accepted at Medium assurance level.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-f1717-static-compression-bending-claim-001",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-fea-pedicle-screw-ensemble-v1",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/nagaraja-f1717-lab1-experimental-n6",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/nagaraja-f1717-lab2-experimental-n5"
  ],
  "hasValidationResult": [
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-result-001",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "ASTM F1717 compression-bending FEA vs. experiment comparison — N=11 constructs, two laboratories"
    }
  ],
  "wasDerivedFrom": "https://doi.org/10.1115/1.4042912",
